# Force LF for files executed inside Linux containers. Without this, a Windows
# checkout with the default core.autocrlf=true rewrites LF -> CRLF on disk, and
# /bin/sh inside the container reads `set -e\r` as an illegal option.
*.sh        text eol=lf
Dockerfile* text eol=lf
*.yml       text eol=lf
*.yaml      text eol=lf
*.conf      text eol=lf
